## What’s included in the report

The report compares your recruitment data for this cycle with the same point in the previous cycle. It also includes national-level data.

You’ll find information on:

- Number of candidates who have submitted applications
- Number of candidates with an offer
- Proportion of candidates with an offer
- Number of candidates who have accepted an offer
- Number of deferrals
- Number of candidates rejected
- Proportion of candidates waiting more than 30 days for a response

